<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des F. Smidlins,
                                <expan>fleischak<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Smidlin für uns besandt und
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede gesaczt; so steet ewr schrift
                        und sein rede ungeleich. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dewcht ewch oder
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>,
                        daz ir <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Smidlein icht
                                <expan>zuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett, so wellen wir ewch
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                            <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan></add>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>p<ex>ur</ex>ificac<ex>i</ex>o<ex>n</ex>is</expan> Marie
                                <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>.</ab>
